  <brief_title>VITRO-Trial. B Vitamins and the Secondary Prevention of Venous Thrombosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Homocysteine Lowering by B Vitamins and the Secondary Prevention of Deep-Vein Thrombosis and Pulmonary Embolism. A Randomized, Placebo-Controlled, Double Blind Trial.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
