  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  objectively confirmed proximal deep-vein thrombosis or pulmonary embolism

          -  idiopathic thrombosis (i.e. absence of major risk factors (major surgery, known
             malignant disease, pregnancy and puerperium or immobility for more than three weeks)

          -  age between 20 to 80 years

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  obligatory use of vitamin B
      </textblock>
